These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice
There 2 different types of food: kale, tomato
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, woodworking
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: scientific, western
1. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the person eating tomato##8
2. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
3. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | juice     | 7up      |
| Food          | tomato | kale    |
| Hobby         | woodworking   | dancing |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific  | western      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, water
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, photography
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, doctor
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, airplane
1. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the left of the analyst##5
3. the doctor is not to the right of the analyst##8
4. the person driving the car is not the person who's hobby is photography##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | lemonade        | water    |
| Hobby       | video-games         | photography |
| Job         | doctor | analyst   |
| Transport   | car               | airplane  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: family, animation
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, d&b
There are 2 different nationalities: spanish, italian
2 different pets are kept: pony, lizard
1. the spanish is in an odd position##4
2. the italian is not to the right of the owner of the lizard##8
3. the fan of trance is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | family       | animation |
| Music-Genre   | trance       | d&b    |
| Nationality   | spanish | italian |
| Pet           | pony        | lizard   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
