The people have 2 different jobs:  videographer, fisherman
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, british
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, bus
1. the canadian is somewhere to the right of the fisherman##5
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
3. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | filmmaking  |
| Job           | fisherman  | videographer |
| Nationality   | british | canadian   |
| Transport     | bus   | helicopter |

