.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-10::.
There 2 different types of food: apricot, blueberry
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, security-guard
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, jet-ski
1. the person eating apricot is not to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##8
2. the person driving the van is the person driving the van##1
3. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5
4. the person driving the van is not to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##8
5. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the left of the person eating blueberry##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
| Food        | apricot | blueberry            |
| Hobby       | rock-climbing | sudoku              |
| Job         | nurse  | security-guard |
| Transport   | van     | jet-ski         |

